14:48.350 --> 14:50.511
Thank you for
coming in, Caitlin.
No,

14:50.550 --> 14:52.347
thank you--
this is so cool.

14:52.390 --> 14:54.153
Um, a very
impressive resume.

14:54.190 --> 14:57.956
You did a summer
at Wyler & Wolf in New York.

14:57.990 --> 15:00.322
