18:36.480 --> 18:37.504
Um...

18:37.550 --> 18:39.677
the... I'm sorry, I-I...

18:39.710 --> 18:40.813
Uh, could you repeat the...

18:40.850 --> 18:42.215
At this meeting...

18:42.250 --> 18:44.343
We need to cut him off;
