19:09.810 --> 19:10.845
Why?

19:10.880 --> 19:12.575
Because I want something.

19:12.610 --> 19:13.577
What?

19:13.620 --> 19:15.576
Freedom.

19:15.620 --> 19:18.509
He'll testify if we free him?

19:18.550 --> 19:21.451
With good behavior,
he's got two years
left on his sentence.

19:21.490 --> 19:24.459
He says that he has something
to offer the State's Attorney.

19:24.490 --> 19:26.481
Evidence _on
drugs in prison.

19:29.430 --> 19:31.591
I think I can find a way
to get around

19:31.630 --> 19:33.461
the private school
money situation.

19:33.500 --> 19:35.536
Hold on, Margie. Hold on.

19:35.570 --> 19:36.798
Well, thank you.
No problem.

19:36.840 --> 19:39.604
So, uh, how are the
interviews going?

19:39.640 --> 19:41.631
Great. I reinterviewed
my top two ch0ices,

