20:34.860 --> 20:36.748
Okay. So...

20:36.800 --> 20:39.360
our good friends
from Lockhart/Gardner...

20:39.400 --> 20:39.968
And Monty & Columbech.

20:40.000 --> 20:41.433
Yes.

20:41.470 --> 20:43.665
They have an offer
to make us in trade

20:43.710 --> 20:45.666
for releasing the wife-killer,
Colin Sweeney.

20:45.710 --> 20:46.961
DIANE: The
defensive killer

20:47.010 --> 20:48.329
of his stalker,
Colin Sweeney.

20:48.380 --> 20:49.938
