21:45.430 --> 21:48.536
One's a painter, one's a writer,
one teaches at the Sorbonne.

21:48.570 --> 21:49.935
Really?

21:49.970 --> 21:51.403
That's in France, isn't it?

21:51.440 --> 21:53.328
Hmm.

22:02.480 --> 22:06.484
Okay, I talked to Peter,
and he has a counteroffer.

22:06.520 --> 22:08.351
DIANE:
Okay. What counteroffer?

22:08.390 --> 22:09.687
CARY:
Donny Pike.

22:09.720 --> 22:11.779
Senior acting member
of the Aryan Warlords.

22:11.830 --> 22:13.388
He's finishing up
a five year stretch

22:13.430 --> 22:14.556
at Pine Creek Penitentiary.

22:14.600 --> 22:16.124
ALICIA:
Oh, come on.

22:16.160 --> 22:18.720
The most dangerous man
in the Illinois system?

22:18.770 --> 22:20.635
CARY:
Yes, he is.

22:20.670 --> 22:21.898
And a confidante
of Colin Sweeney.

22:21.940 --> 22:25.762
Mr. Sweeney gives him stock tips
and Pike gives him protection.

22:25.810 --> 22:27.801
You want Sweeney
to testify against him?

22:27.840 --> 22:30.673
