turn against him was murdered.

22:33.750 --> 22:35.672
Yes. Well,

22:35.720 --> 22:37.881
we've learned from our mistakes.

22:37.920 --> 22:40.115
Here, you can keep this.

22:48.500 --> 22:51.128
GENEVA:
I was the ASA
who won that plea bargain

22:51.170 --> 22:52.899
and you're really considering
reversing it?

22:52.930 --> 22:54.830
Not reversing it.
He's served two years.

22:54.870 --> 22:56.394
For killing a woman.

22:56.440 --> 22:59.534
No, involuntary manslaughter,
with good behavior.

22:59.570 --> 23:01.674
GENEVA:
This is Colin Sweeney
we're talking about.

23:01.710 --> 23:02.836
The public knows his name.

23:02.880 --> 23:04.768
If we release him,
we'll be crucified.

23:04.810 --> 23:05.902
_Not if we're
usmg him to stop

23:05.950 --> 23:07.918
a neo-Nazi from committing
more murders from prison.

23:07.950 --> 23:10.111
What do you think, Imani?

23:11.620 --> 23:13.850
I think it's worth it

23:13.890 --> 23:15.915
if we can stop this
white supremacist.

23:15.960 --> 23:17.655
Yeah. If you stop him.

23:17.690 --> 23:19.885
But if Colin Sweeney
takes the stand,

23:19.930 --> 23:22.524
I don't know a jury in the
world who would trust him.

23:22.560 --> 23:23.822
Okay, we're going
to make the deal.

23:23.870 --> 23:25.758
GENEVA:
Peter, this is a mistake.

23:25.800 --> 23:27.768
You'll be the man
who released O.J.

23:27.800 --> 23:29.688
Would you make the deal
if it was just anybody?

23:29.740 --> 23:30.832
But it's not just anybody.

23:30.870 --> 23:33.065
I know, but if it were...

23:33.110 --> 23:34.839
would you make the deal?

23:34.880 --> 23:37.872
Two years left
on an involuntary manslaughter?

23:38.910 --> 23:40.548
There's your answer.

23:40.580 --> 23:42.810
But Geneva makes a good point
about the testimony.

23:42.850 --> 23:44.681
We're going to
make the deal,

23:44.720 --> 23:46.085
but he's got to give us more.

23:46.120 --> 23:47.451
CARY:
What more?

23:47.490 --> 23:49.481
A wire.

23:52.090 --> 23:54.058
Eli.

23:54.100 --> 23:56.557
What have you got?

23:56.600 --> 23:59.489
Keynote address at the
Democratic Convention.

23:59.530 --> 24:01.498
They were going
with Spellman,

24:01.540 --> 24:02.837
but he has an issue
opposmg gay marriage,

24:02.870 --> 24:05.134
so I got you the hearing
with Donna Brazile.

24:06.170 --> 24:07.876
