24:11.950 --> 24:14.839
Look, you don't have to decide
about running for governor.

24:14.880 --> 24:17.519
Just take the meeting,
sweep her off her feet,

24:17.550 --> 24:18.949
keep hitting the
prison thing.

24:18.990 --> 24:20.082
That's your
selling point.

24:20.120 --> 24:22.884
Huh.
What?

24:22.920 --> 24:25.457
I may be in the news this week.

24:26.290 --> 24:29.054
Okay.

24:29.100 --> 24:32.592
A plea bargain that could gain
a lot of attention.

24:32.630 --> 24:34.530
Can you delay it?

24:34.570 --> 24:36.891
I could.

24:36.940 --> 24:38.999
But I won't.

24:43.580 --> 24:45.707
I would love to give
that keynote speech.

24:45.750 --> 24:48.514
Then don't get
in the news.

24:48.550 --> 24:50.916
And what does Kalinda Sharma
have against you?

24:52.650 --> 24:53.856
The investigator at
Lockhart/ Gardner,

24:53.890 --> 24:55.016
she won't do any
work for you.

24:55.060 --> 24:56.186
What's that about?

24:58.190 --> 25:00.181
I don't know.

25:02.960 --> 25:04.564
Really? I didn't know that.
Is she good?

25:04.600 --> 25:05.897
Caitlin?

25:05.930 --> 25:08.637
Yes. It's just...

25:08.670 --> 25:10.809
