25:10.840 --> 25:11.909
Who's the better lavwer?

25:11.940 --> 25:12.907
Well, they're both good.

25:12.940 --> 25:14.703
It's just...

25:14.740 --> 25:16.037
I don't know,
there's something about Martha.

25:16.080 --> 25:17.672
I like her.

25:17.710 --> 25:20.201
And Caitlin
is a classic "C" student.

25:20.250 --> 25:21.569
Well, you know what they say:

25:21.620 --> 25:22.871
"A" students make great
professors,

25:22.920 --> 25:24.581
"B" students make great judges,

25:24.620 --> 25:25.939
and "C" students make partner.

25:25.990 --> 25:26.911
GRACE (over phone):
Mom!

25:26.950 --> 25:28.884
Okay, I got to go.

25:28.920 --> 25:29.955
Thanks, Will.

25:29.990 --> 25:32.720
