not to be friends with me?

25:32.760 --> 25:33.954
Did I...?

25:34.000 --> 25:35.228
Did you tell her
not to be my friend?

25:35.260 --> 25:37.967
No, I told her that I wanted her

25:38.000 --> 25:39.126
to concentrate _more
on your studies.

25:39.170 --> 25:40.637
Why, what did she say?

25:40.670 --> 25:41.967
Nothing.

25:42.000 --> 25:44.935
