25:57.080 --> 25:59.139
Because she's my friend.

25:59.190 --> 26:00.782
No, she's you're tutor.

26:00.820 --> 26:02.048
I'm paying her.

26:02.090 --> 26:04.729
Why can't she be both?

26:06.760 --> 26:09.354
Because it's unprofessional.

26:09.400 --> 26:11.197
It's...

26:11.230 --> 26:12.993
I don't have friends, Mom.

26:13.030 --> 26:15.066
